question: 7!! 🎃👻
answer:
send me a number and I’ll tell you a Theonsa headcanon!

They are the kind of couple that loves to do matching costumes together and they often switch the genders of the costumes, like Theon going as the mermaid (he loooves to show off his six pack and, of course, Sansa is not going to complain about it) and Sansa going as the pirate.

Also, Sansa absolutely loves Halloween since she was a little girl, they decorate their flat together and make all kind of recipes that contains pumpkin in a way or another. 

As for the place, the Starks siblings take turns to host their annual Halloween party, tho everyone loves Arya’s parties since she makes the most frightening ones (and being scared is one of Sansa’s fav excuses to snuggle Theon, although she doesn’t need one, but he does not tell her that.)

Sorry for taking so long to reply, I’ve been busy with exams :(

summary: Until Sansa stans can admit that Sansa bullied Arya and contributed to her sister's low self-esteem, they can't call themselves...
body: Until Sansa stans can admit that Sansa bullied Arya and contributed to her sister’s low self-esteem, they can’t call themselves Arya fans. Hell, they can’t even call themselves Sansa fans since they deny that there’s any complexity in their self-insert. Oh, and they also can’t claim to have any comprehension skills either since Sansa’s bullying is canon and it was a significant part of the very reason GRRM created her. It’s not even subtle or at all disputable.
